{
  "stem": "1413.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, to make a long story short, on Friday night, they picked some people who didn't have to go to Germany on account they needed the good workers in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was the second one-- one above me-- I have to admit it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He got some identification that he didn't have to go to the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was the second.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Sure enough, that Sunday [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] my father and wife came to Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, like I said, I was spared to go to Germany, or sent to wherever they send me to.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that Sunday morning, when my father and my wife came, the next day they want to send them away-- away from Holland to Germany, or Poland-- wherever they send them.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went up to the Germans there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I told them-- no, I was-- I said to my father, and my wife, and my aunt, what I told you before, if you go, I go.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we're sitting in the train, and I said to whoever it was, I was spared-- the Friday night.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I am not supposed to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I want my father, my aunt-- but I called her my mother at the time, because my mother died.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the story about my aunt, even though she looks like my father, and my wife-- I was taken off the train with my wife, with my father, and my aunt.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You've got me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I had an ID.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I was not supposed to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my main goal was not for me alone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I got my father off-- I got my father, my wife, and my aunt.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
